Package: dimsprepr
Title: End-to-End Preprocessing of Direct-Injection Metabolomics Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("John Lennon", "Calorio", , "jllcalorio@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A complete, reproducible preprocessing pipeline for
    direct-injection mass spectrometry (DIMS) metabolomics data — missing
    value filtering, imputation, signal drift and batch correction,
    normalization, transformation, scaling, and quality filtering — in a
    single reproducible pipeline. Supports multi-method mode: normalization,
    transformation, and scaling methods may each be supplied as character
    vectors, and the pipeline computes every combination while running the
    shared preprocessing steps only once.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
